original_font_information.trademark: Archivo is a trademark of Omnibus-Type.
original_font_information.description: Archivo is a grotesque sans serif typeface family from Omnibus-Type. It was originally designed for highlights and headlines. This family is reminiscent of late nineteenth century American typefaces.
